## GoBP PROJECT STRUCTURE (sketch)

```
gobp/core/     graph, search, indexes, graph_algorithms, mutator, init, …
gobp/mcp/      server, dispatcher, parser, batch_parser, tools/
gobp/schema/   core_nodes.yaml, core_edges.yaml (v2 taxonomy post–Wave 17A02); core_nodes_v2.yaml / core_edges_v2.yaml retained as sources; *_v1.yaml backups
tests/         test_*.py — full suite is the gate
waves/         wave_*_brief.md
docs/          guides (only edit per Brief + R12)
```

