## GoBP MCP — KEY ACTIONS

```
READ:   overview: find: get: explore: suggest: template: template_batch:
        related: code: invariants: tests: decisions: recent: sections:
WRITE:  session:start/end create: upsert: lock: batch quick: edge:
        delete: retype: merge: import: recompute:
MAINTAIN: validate: stats: refresh:
```

AI User Guide: `docs/GoBP_AI_USER_GUIDE.md`

